#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
=begin pod
=head2 get-deltas

Extracts the scroll deltas of a scroll event.

The deltas will be zero unless the scroll direction
is C<GDK_SCROLL_SMOOTH>.

For the representation unit of these deltas, see
L<.get-unit()|#get-unit>.

=begin code
method get-deltas ( Num() $delta-x, Num() $delta-y )
=end code

=item $delta-x; (transfer ownership: full) return location for x scroll delta.
=item $delta-y; (transfer ownership: full) return location for y scroll delta.

=begin comment

=head2 Example
# Example for get-deltas

=end comment

=end pod

